.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, dressmaker, security-guard, software-developer
4 different games are played: billiard, poker, backgammon, chess
1. the person playing billiard is the dressmaker##1
2. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person playing poker is somewhere to the left of the dressmaker##5
4. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
5. the person playing poker is on the left of the coach##1
6. the software-developer and the person playing chess have the same parity positions##9
7. the security-guard is on the left or right of the coach##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | software-developer | security-guard | coach  | dressmaker |
| Music-Genre   | backgammon             | poker          | chess | billiard    |

