4. the american and the person who's hobby is card-games have the same parity positions##9
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking and the american have different parity positions##9
6. the indian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
7. the thai is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
8. the person who's hobby is photography is not to the right of the thai##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
