2. the owner of the hamster is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the person playing backgammon is not the owner of the fish##6
6. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person playing backgammon##5
7. the person playing chess and the owner of the rabbit have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | chess | backgammon | whist | scrabble |
| Pet     | hamster     | mouse     | rabbit     | fish    |

