1. the person driving the trike is not to the left of the alhambra-smoker##8
2. the bongani-smoker and the person driving the trike have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
4. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
5. the swisher-smoker is somewhere between the person driving the snowmobile and the person driving the trike##7
6. the bongani-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | chaman | alhambra   | swisher | bongani |
| Transport   | tram   | snowmobile | car    | trike      |

