.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
House: art-deco, victorian, cape-cod, ranch-style
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, italian, turkish
1. the ranch-style house is not the turkish##6
2. the turkish is not to the right of the canadian##8
3. the cape-cod house is not to the left of the ranch-style house##8
4. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
5. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the italian##3
6. the turkish is on the far left##1
7. the canadian is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
8. the art-deco house is the colombian##1
9. the ranch-style house and the canadian have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | victorian   | ranch-style    | cape-cod | art-deco    |
| Nationality   | turkish | canadian | italian   | colombian |

