.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, milk, mirinda
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, august, july, october
 1. the person drinking lemonade and the person who's birthday is in july have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking 7up##7
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 5. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
 7. the person drinking mirinda and the person who's birthday is in august have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking mirinda is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | 7up  | mirinda | milk  | lemonade |
| Music-Genre   | october | july     | september | august     |

